text: Vic Clark is a retired American football coach. He served as the head football coach at Thomas More College in Crestview Hills, Kentucky from 1990 to 1998 and at Rockford University in Rockford, Illinois from 2000 to 2002, compiling a career college football record of 71–48. ==Head coaching record== ==References== Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people Category:Thomas More Saints football coaches Category:Rockford Regents football coaches
